<blockquote style="margin:0 0 0 30px;border:none;padding:0px"><span style="line-height:21px">
<p style="font-size:15px">Blackstone Academy is proud to have been a RIDE Commended School. This <a href="http://www.ride.ri.gov/InformationAccountability/Accountability/Award-WinningSchools.aspx" target="_blank"><font color="#660000">commendation</font></a> is a reflection of our strong school culture, the academic success and growth of our students, and our commitment to engaging diverse learners despite their past or present challenges. The majority of our students go on to higher education and will be the first in their family to do so.</p>
</span></blockquote>
