<hr>BACS has been a <font color="#0b5394"> <a href="https://www.google.com/edu/" target="_blank"><font color="#0b5394">G Suite for Education</font></a></font> school since 2016 and is a one-to-one Chromebook school. This platform allows for blended learning opportunities, improved collaboration and sharing, and increased security. <br><hr></span><hr>
