<div style="text-align:center"><font color="#351c75" face="georgia, serif" size="3"><b>5 Easy Steps to Complete Your Family Survey</b></font></div>
<div><font color="#351c75" face="georgia, serif" size="3"><br></font></div>
<div><font color="#351c75" face="georgia, serif" size="3"><b>Step 1:</b> Visit surveys.panoramaed.com/ride</font></div>
<div><font color="#351c75" face="georgia, serif" size="3"><b>Step 2:</b> Enter your school’s unique access code. This will be a school identifying code,</font></div>
<div><font color="#351c75" face="georgia, serif" size="3">followed by the word “family” (all lower case). For example: 12345family</font></div>
<div><font color="#351c75" face="georgia, serif" size="3"><b>Step 3: </b>On the Welcome page, your school’s survey will be displayed. Click “Start</font></div>
<div><font color="#351c75" face="georgia, serif" size="3">Surveys”</font></div>
<div><font color="#351c75" face="georgia, serif" size="3"><b>Step 4:</b> You have now accessed the family survey. In the top left hand corner, there is a</font></div>
<div><font color="#351c75" face="georgia, serif" size="3">drop down menu. Select English or Spanish or Portuguese.</font></div>
<div><font color="#351c75" face="georgia, serif" size="3"><b>Step 5:</b> For each question, select the answers that best apply to your experience and</font></div>
<div><font color="#351c75" face="georgia, serif" size="3">beliefs. Once finished, click “Submit,” and you are done!</font></div>
</div>
<br><div style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><font size="4">Link: <a href="http://surveys.panoramaed.com/ride" style="color:rgb(17,85,204)" target="_blank">surveys.panoramaed.com/ride</a><br></font></div>
